data.description: Investors wanted!  Seller needs a 1 yr lease back. This ranch style home sits on over 1/2 acre lot wooded lot, and features 4 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, including 4 car garage. The craftsman's style home been completely renovated including upgraded lightning, tile accents, hardwood floors, and extensive trim accents. Main level boasts open foyer, formal dining room, family room with double sided fireplace with view to keeping room, eat-in breakfast room with view to large fenced backyard and covered back porch. Kitchen boasts granite counter tops, undermount black sink, tile back splash, dry-bar, gas range, SS dishwasher, and built-in microwave with range. Master suite offers separate floor plan, double vanity, separate soaking tub, stand-up shower, private toilet room, and large walk-in closet. Spacious secondary bedrooms with full bathroom and generous closet space. Detached garage offers mezzanine storage above. All this is sought after Highland Park swim/tennis subdivision.
